Dragonheir Scion	KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion	CATEGORY:Archetype	TYPE:Archetype.FighterArchetype	PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Fighter_Archetype_ClassSkills=true,Fighter_Archetype_Bravery=true,Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining1=true,Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining2=true,Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining3=true,Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining4=true,Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining=true,Fighter_Archetype_ArmorMastery=true,Fighter_Archetype_WeaponMastery=true,Fighter_Archetype_BonusFeat1=true,Fighter_Archetype_BonusFeat2=true,Fighter_Archetype_BonusFeat4=true]	DESC:Dragonheir scions are the martially inclined humanoid descendants of those influenced by draconic power. Unlike their sorcerous brethren, dragonheir scions manifest their heritage in ways more suited to strength of arms and skill with steel than arcane energies. Those who follow this path are often the children of mighty dragon-blooded sorcerers and others who drew energy from their dragon blood, though they themselves might not exhibit spellcasting ability.	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Class Skills|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Bloodline|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Eldritch Strikes|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Fearful Might|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Defenses|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=3	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Strike|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=3	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Presence|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=5	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Wings|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=15	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Might of Wyrms|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=20	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Fighter	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_Bravery|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining1|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining2|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining3|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining4|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_ArmorTraining|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_ArmorMastery|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_WeaponMastery|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_BonusFeat1|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_BonusFeat2|true	FACT:Fighter_Archetype_BonusFeat4|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_Bravery|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_ArmorTraining1|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_ArmorTraining2|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_ArmorTraining3|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_ArmorTraining4|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_ArmorTraining|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_ArmorMastery|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_WeaponMastery|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_BonusFeat1|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_BonusFeat2|true	FACT:Fighter_CF_BonusFeat4|true

