Draconic Bloodline	KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Bloodline	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:Each dragonheir scion can draw her lineage back to the influence of a great draconic progenitor. At 1st level, a dragonheir scion must select one of the chromatic or metallic dragon types. Once chosen, this cannot be changed. A number of dragonheir scion’s abilities deal damage and grant resistances based on her dragon type, as noted below. If a dragonheir scion takes a level in another class that grants a bloodline, the bloodlines must be of the same type, even if that means that the bloodline of one of the classes must change. Subject to GM discretion, the dragonheir scion can change her former bloodline to make them conform.		BONUS:VAR|POOL_FADS_DraconicBloodline|1	DEFINE:POOL_FADS_DraconicBloodline|0	ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Black)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Black		ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Blue)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Blue		ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Green)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Green		ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Red)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Red		ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (White)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ White		ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Brass)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Brass		ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Bronze)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Bronze	ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Copper)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Copper	ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Bloodline (Gold)|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dragonheir Scion Draconic Bloodline ~ Gold		ASPECT:NAME|Dra