Eldritch Strikes		KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Eldritch Strikes		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 1st level, a dragonheir scion gains Arcane Strike as a bonus feat. She does not need to meet its prerequisites. This ability replaces the bonus feat gained at 1st level.	ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Arcane Strike
Fearful Might		KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Fearful Might		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:At 1st level, a dragonheir scion gains a +1 bonus on Intimidate checks to demoralize a foe. This bonus increases to +2 at 6th level and by an additional 1 every 4 fighter levels thereafter to a maximum of +5 at 18th level. This ability replaces bravery.		BONUS:SITUATION|Intimidate=To demoralize|1+floor((FighterLVL-2)/4)
Draconic Defenses		KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Defenses	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 3rd level, a dragonheir scion gains a +1 natural armor bonus and energy resistance 5 against her energy type. At 7th level, this increases to a +2 natural armor bonus and energy resistance 10; at 13th level, it increases to a +3 natural armor bonus and energy resistance 20. This ability replaces armor training 1, 2, and 3.	DEFINE:DSDD_ProgressionLVL|0		BONUS:VAR|DSDD_ProgressionLVL|1+(FighterLVL>=7)+(FighterLVL>=13)+(FighterLVL>=20)	DEFINE:DSDD_EnergyResistance|0	BONUS:VAR|DSDD_EnergyResistance|5+if(DSDD_ProgressionLVL>=2,5,0)+if(DSDD_ProgressionLVL>=3,10,0)|PREVARLT:DSDD_ProgressionLVL,4	DEFINE:DSDD_NaturalArmor|0		BONUS:VAR|DSDD_NaturalArmor|min(3,DSDD_ProgressionLVL)	BONUS:VAR|AC_Natural_Armor|DSDD_NaturalArmor|TYPE=DSDD
Draconic Strike		KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Strike		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 3rd level, whenever the dragonheir scion damages a target with an attack augmented by Arcane Strike, the attack deals an additional 1d4 points of damage of the dragonheir scion’s energy type. This ability replaces the bonus feat gained at 3rd level.	ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Strikes (Acid)|PREVAREQ:DSDD_Type_Acid,1	ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Strikes (Cold)|PREVAREQ:DSDD_Type_Cold,1	ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Strikes (Electricity)|PREVAREQ:DSDD_Type_Electricity,1	ASPECT:NAME|Draconic Strikes (Fire)|PREVAREQ:DSDD_Type_Fire,1
Draconic Presence		KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Draconic Presence	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 5th level, the dragonheir scion receives Dazzling Display as a bonus feat. She does not need a weapon in hand to use this ability, and can use it as a standard action. This ability replaces the bonus feat gained at 5th level.	ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Dazzling Display
Wings				KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Dragonheir Scion ~ Wings			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 15th level, a dragonheir scion can grow leathery dragon wings from her back as a standard action, granting her a fly speed of 60 feet with average maneuverability. She can dismiss the wings as a free action. This ability replaces armor training 4 and armor mastery.	MOVE:Fly,60	BONUS:VAR|Maneuverability|3
